Description: Dropbear SSH server for OpenAPS root access.
 Bundles the dropbear 2012.55 (Debian wheezy, armhf/glibc 2.15) server and
 helper binaries (dropbear, dropbearkey, dbclient, dropbearconvert) plus an
 rcS.d init script that starts dropbear on :22 at boot. Root login is allowed
 by BOTH public key and password. The postinst generates an RSA host key if
 absent and enforces dropbear StrictModes ownership on /home/root and
 /home/root/.ssh.
